data.description: Located off of I-2 in Mercedes and a 5 minute drive to the Rio Grande Premium Outlets, this 3 bed/2 bath is a great home with automated sprinkler system throughout the whole yard. Feel welcomed into the open living and kitchen area with a pantry, chef's kitchen with granite countertops & induction top stove with air-fryer in oven. Along with a spacious primary suite, take advantage of granite countertops with Jack & Jill sinks and a walk-in closet. Some of the home upgrades include whole house plantation shutters, concrete porch perfect for grilling & a screened back porch that makes cooking and entertaining a breeze. The privacy fenced backyard features 1 workshop with porch swing, tile floors and heating and air, while the other is perfect for storage. The 2 car garage includes a fully mechanized screen door & the backyard fence includes a gate on each side. Don't miss it, check out this unique and updated home located right off the highway. *Sheds and appliances will be conveying.
